  "detailed_description": "-It's dangerous to leave your child home alone at night, <br>and if that dangerous thing happened to your child, would you be able to handle it? <br>And what if the kidnapper is a demonic clown? <br>They need your help now. <br><strong>Defeat the demonic clown and survive!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a fantastical, high-quality graphical map to find your child.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/b989633480a949d0bd9009379d884029.poster.avif?t=1714452531\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/b989633480a949d0bd9009379d884029.webm?t=1714452531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/b989633480a949d0bd9009379d884029.mp4?t=1714452531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/1a0a4d1180287336acfd717d4f0db2c4.poster.avif?t=1714452531\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/1a0a4d1180287336acfd717d4f0db2c4.webm?t=1714452531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/1a0a4d1180287336acfd717d4f0db2c4.mp4?t=1714452531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a large map to progress through the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Communicate with characters to advance the story.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/7ebcad23f70a4290a24b32660e347ceb.poster.avif?t=1714452531\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/7ebcad23f70a4290a24b32660e347ceb.webm?t=1714452531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/7ebcad23f70a4290a24b32660e347ceb.mp4?t=1714452531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Communicate with characters, find evidence, and progress the story.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find the guns and defeat our enemies.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/e62d221b11bc83e97adf0438fcf48525.poster.avif?t=1714452531\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/e62d221b11bc83e97adf0438fcf48525.webm?t=1714452531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907630/extras/e62d221b11bc83e97adf0438fcf48525.mp4?t=1714452531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Kill to not die. You have to survive!",
